				I realized that its much more easier and protocol to have multiples tables rather than one table. Im guessing its much more easier to have a column for different values than combining it in one column. My question is what if I am designing a page that has a fixed info and I will always need to pull those info together. For example I have a column called T-Shirt Colors under the table CL..." />
		
		
		
